@node Standard "DayDream BBS FAQ - Modem configurations - Universal standard modem)"

This configuration should work for ALL Hayes compatible modems. If all else
fails, try this.

IO_BAUD....... 38400
IO_DEVICE..... serial.device
IO_PREINIT.... ~+++~ATZ|
IO_OFFHOOK.... ATH1|
IO_ANSWER..... ATA|
IO_INIT....... ATZ|
IO_AFTERCALL.. ~ATH|
IO_OK......... OK
IO_RING....... RING
IO_NOCARRIER.. NO CARRIER
IO_CONNECT.... CONNECT

or you could try to use:
IO_INIT....... AT&F|

to restore factory settings at each reset.

@endnode


